{"tid":1310384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"已經有六萬五千人聯署促請美國國會通過《香港人權及民主法》！","createTime":"2019-07-12T15:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-13T16:33:02.000Z","uid":2429,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d47f86ddc95f6c57c2060c84719d12bf739c0216","tid":1310384,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:48:45.000Z","msg":"已經有六萬五千人聯署促請美國國會通過《香港人權及民主法》！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要求美國向北京施壓，在2020年度的香港立法會換屆選舉實行全面普選，否則制裁相關中港官員！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n三步曲︰<br />\n1. 簽名<br />\n2. 在 Email confirm<br />\n3. 廣傳開去<br />\n<br />\n尚欠三萬五千人！請大家幫手聯署並分享！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR3oH8TmACJzqoWhfJPHenIX1hy872WND3Z9RozQP8f1Mv5PMF77VnbhWNo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3oH8TmACJzqoWhfJPHenIX1hy872WND3Z9RozQP8f1Mv5PMF77VnbhWNo&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=f0cae301\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-pass-bill-hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act?fbclid=IwAR3oH8TmACJzqoWhfJPHenIX1hy872WND3Z9RozQP8f1Mv5PMF77VnbhWNo</a>[/quote]<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bNFY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bNFY6E.jpg&h=0e3ff068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJqqMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJqqMr.jpg&h=d5937562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUnCgTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUnCgTg.jpg&h=4d401a96&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KAgxru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KAgxru.jpg&h=a97e178b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUtoye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUtoye.jpg&h=36d1db08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gBzi6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gBzi6w.jpg&h=067ee06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，不撤不散︰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫暴<br />\n五、實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"c27e04f378986c6a6c8361c08f1e659ae180708b","tid":1310384,"uid":38804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"我聽日光復上水，<br />\n後日去沙田野餐"},{"pid":"095bc07fe0bc90db0ff32d54210666f55773bd44","tid":1310384,"uid":34515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:53:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個位嚟<br />\n鐘教授個研究所仲差300萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果有興趣捐助鍾庭耀成立嘅香港民意研究所，有以下三個方法：<br />\n<br />\n1）去網站 <a href=\"http://pori.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpori.hk&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=2040a051\" target=\"_blank\">http://pori.hk</a> 捐款，可以用信用卡或者 PayPal<br />\n<br />\n2)  寄支票去香港民意研究所，地址：「香港數碼港道100號數碼港2座12樓1205至1208室Smart-Space 2」。支票抬頭寫「香港民意研究所」<br />\n<br />\n3）如捐款超過一萬元又唔想俾中介收手續費，寄電郵去donation.hkpop@gmail.com <br />\n香港民意研究所會俾個銀行戶口你。</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKjdQbz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKjdQbz.gif&h=ae508f19&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cdjmeDe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcdjmeDe.gif&h=7704431c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E8J2Jwz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE8J2Jwz.gif&h=2e948b2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmtRBRA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmtRBRA.gif&h=c4802df2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/79hnJwA.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F79hnJwA.gif&h=a60a60ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2d67d4fd802ab15f87accc5f14e782fe754c1a5","tid":1310384,"uid":35104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd93cb4db0bc264ededbc52c2bb7640f1d365fb5","tid":1310384,"uid":44174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:54:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cc81fa66669b63d8f780b27fb6cad08b8112a35f","tid":1310384,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:57:24.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署link在此：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=5cbbdb2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會快推《香港人權及民主法案》<br />\n填完後可能半小時以上信箱才會有認證信<br />\n麻煩大家注意一下信箱"},{"pid":"f12c3164ba9086235946cb3b2c9db4fd93268673","tid":1310384,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-12T15:58:12.000Z","msg":"白宮聯署link在此：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XOf0aj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOf0aj&d=f11PFKDsvG%2B7MRfNo%2B80BZktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=5cbbdb2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XOf0aj</a><br />\n<br />\n請求美國國會快推《香港人權及民主法案》<br />\n填完後可能半小時以上信箱才會有認證信<br />\n麻煩大家注意一下信箱"},{"pid":"ccf7caf17ec920d848cc14bf20df5c4ead95b914","tid":1310384,"uid":216253,"like":0,"disl